item.title: SoftLayer_Account_Shipment_Item
item.description: SoftLayer_Account_Shipment_Item Service Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Account_Shipment_Item data type contains information relating to a shipment’s item. Basic information such as addresses, the shipment courier, and any tracking information for as shipment is accessible with this data type. Local createDate Type: dateTime description The description of the shipping item. Type: string id The unique id of the shipping item. Type: integer
